<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu śakavarṣaṁbulu 
<lb n="2"/>1172 nēṁṭi sādhāraṇa saṁvatsa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ramu pauṣya bahula 15 Ādi<unclear>tya</unclear> 
